I’m editing the app-side sync bridge now. The changes are focused: route user messages through `AppSyncStore`/`SyncNode`, remove the legacy permission/question fallback in `ops`, and teach the direct part renderer how to carry question-block metadata so the UI can answer it over the v3 channel.
