I audited the current branch, found the app still had legacy fallbacks on the critical v3 path, and tightened that path so user messages plus permission/question resolution now go through AppSyncStore/SyncNode. I also added focused tests around the new direct part mapping and the stricter ops routing.
  ✓ Audit current happy-sync/CLI/app/server wiring against the refactor spec and identify concrete failures
  ✓ Implement the missing or broken refactor pieces without overwriting unrelated in-progress changes
  ✓ Run targeted verification for the affected packages and confirm remaining gaps, if any
